window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When Ben first bought his starship, he expected to spend the rest of his days joyriding through the universe with his best friend. <br> <br> As the most wanted criminal in a galaxy that’s about to be crushed in the iron fist of an evil tyrant, it’s fair to say things haven’t gone according to plan. Caught up in the middle of a looming intergalactic conflict and rejected by both sides, there’s only one thing left for him to do.<br> <br> Take the biggest risk of his life....<br> <b>And prepare for war.</b></p>"; 
